thought he was a lawyer. He had memorized volumes and volumes of legal proceedings and would quote them as he fought. It seemed reasonable for the skeleton to unmake itself when he advised it that unlicensed exhuming of humanoid remains was a felony (Vicious Mockery). Highwaymen would drop their weapons and surrender themselves to the nearest officer of the law (Suggestion). This was just the power of the law, not anything magical. His "instrument" was a enormous book of case law and he used a gavel as a weapon.